# Stratagem Hero Mobile

###### A Finger-Flicking Tactical Mini-Game for Galactic Peace

- Made by a broke college student preparing for exams. Zero budget. Blurry graphics. Tons of bugs.  
- Somehow found time between liberating the galaxy to recreate the **"Stratagem Hero"** mini-game from the Super Citizen Edition of *Helldivers II*.  
  Will anyone actually like this kind of thing? (Â´I`)

- **If you enjoy the project, feel free to give it a â­! Thanks!**

- **Need art assets? Youâ€™re welcome to take anything from the `resources/` folder.**

- A **fan-made tactical mini-game** inspired by *Helldivers II*, now on Android.  
- Completely offline, no ads, no trackingâ€”just good old tactical fun, anytime, anywhere.

